And, another thread is revived. I welcome it, but will anything change?

In article <C97E81.Aoq@chinet.chinet.com>, schneier@chinet.chinet.com (Bruce Schneier) writes:
|> In article <1993Jun22.104404.1@zodiac.rutgers.edu> leichter@zodiac.rutgers.edu writes:
